        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " together as a group. In these verses the subject is the means of rising (in the world), and the two ways, the one of which leads to error, and the other to life.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "24 The land of the diligent attains to dominion,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "     But slothfulness will become tributary.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
